outputs.output_descr:
Project goal: to reduce local and Greenhouse gases emissions while improving access and quality of public transport services for all residents

Project outputs: 
- Lower emissions from vehicles in Dushanbe, with safety and health quality in mind;
- Increased use of public transport, particularly trolleybuses;
- Integrated land use and urban transport planning at the metropolitan level;
- Increased use of non-motorised modes, including bicycles;
- Institutional transformation of government, businesses and general public to embrace sustainable transport
